Big Brother Naija, BBNaija 2020 housemate, Vee has revealed things Laycon did for her in the reality show. Vee was Laycon’s closest friend in the house and stood up for him during an alteration with Erica. She said Laycon changed her mind about a lot of things and that meeting him was a blessing, explaining that he also saved her from a lot of arguments in the house. She said, ”Laycon has got an inviting spirit, I can see a lot people talking about things our friendship has done to him, what they ain’t saying is what our friendship has done to me. ”He has changed my mind about a lot of things, meeting him in the house is a blessing. ”I could have been worse, a lot more quarrels, but he was there for me too.”